temperature gauge giving off the wrong reading.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine fires can cause complete destruction of the vehicle, injury, or death.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Cooling system failure can cause engine overheating, damage, and failure, leading to a loss of vehicle control and accidents.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering hose can cause fluid to leak, leading to a loss of power steering, and potentially resulting in a fire.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the serpentine belt can cause a loss of power steering, leading to a loss of vehicle control, and potentially resulting in an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering system can cause a loss of vehicle control, leading to an accident.

visible signs of wear or damage to steering components.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause a loss of vehicle control, leading to an accident.

rattling or vibrating sensation when braking
visible signs of wear or damage to brake components.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure to notify vehicle owners of recalls can lead to delayed or missed repairs, potentially resulting in accidents or injuries.
symptoms: frustration with dealership or manufacturer response.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall or catch fire, leading to accidents or injuries.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the PCM can cause the vehicle to stall or shut down, leading to accidents or injuries.
